  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      prescription opioid misuse in chronic pain is a growing public health concern. few studies
      got interested in prevalence of misuse and of opiate use disorder in a population of patients
      with a non cancer chronic pain.

      the investigators analyzed during 3 months opiate misuse and opiate ude disorder in a
      population of patients consulting a center specialized in pain management.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
